{
  "text": "The neuropsychological evaluation consisted in the administration during the same assessment of BRB-NT and D-KEFS ST, in agreement with the original manuals and normative data for Italian population [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and z-scores were considered in the analysis. The failure in one item was defined when the z-score was below 1.5 standard deviation.",
